<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">
	<PropertyGroup>
		<Description>Purpose-bound data protection for Cohesion: interface-first protector contracts (purpose-chain derivation, Protect/Unprotect over spans), AES-256-GCM payloads with versioned key-id headers, HKDF-SHA256 subkey derivation, and a rotating key ring with grace-period unprotect over a pluggable IKeyRepository (file-system default). BCL System.Security.Cryptography only; AOT/trim-safe with zero reflection.</Description>
	</PropertyGroup>
</Project>
